Title: Center CB hand held foam 750ml
Description: A single component, self-expanding polyurethane foam, this Center CB gun-grade fixing foam B3 with CFC-free propellant is supplied ready to use and contains completely harmless propellants. It is suitable for use in the installation of window and door frames, for filling cavities, sealing all openings in roof constructions and creation of soundproof screens. It is additionally ideal for the mounting and sealing of window and door frames, connecting insulation materials, roof constructions, applying soundproofing layers on motors, improving the thermal insulation in a cooling systems and installation of air conditioners.

Title: Center CB anti static foam cleaner 400ml
Description: A unique thick-foaming cleaner, Center CB anti-static foam cleaner lifts, breaks down and removes dirt, grease, stains and soiling from hard surfaces and fabrics. Formulated to help remove static charges, this cleaner can reduce the attraction of dust, ideal for use on electrical equipment. Anti-static foam cleaner is suitable for domestic appliances, worktops, walls, machinery, plant equipment, cabinets, casings, formica, vinyl and leatherette upholstery.
